Package: factorselect
Title: Eigenvalue-Based Estimation of the Number of Factors in Approximate Factor Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jason", "Parker", email = "jparker588@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9227-6976"))
Description: An R package for eigenvalue-based estimation of the number 
    of factors in approximate factor models. Designed to work when either 
    N or T is large, without requiring both dimensions to grow 
    simultaneously.
